{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947650/extras/discordEN.jpg?t=1737084066\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Choppy Cuts, fun and chaos go hand in hand. You can team up with friends to tackle a variety of hairdressing challenges. Work together to create amazing hairstyles and have a blast along the way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udc88<strong>Be Quick!</strong> \ud83d\udc88</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whatever it is, just toss it over \u2014 even the customers! Efficiency is our top priority!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947650/extras/gif01_EN.gif?t=1737084066\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83e\ude92<strong>Team up! </strong>\ud83e\ude92</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ready to go for three stars? Every task demands precision and perfect teamwork. Rally your friends and show off your team spirit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947650/extras/gif02_EN.gif?t=1737084066\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2702\ufe0f<strong>Snip and clip! </strong>\u2702\ufe0f</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pick your hairstylist character, wield a range of unique tools, and journey through diverse universes, leaving no hair uncut!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947650/extras/\u9759\u6001\u56fe_EN.png?t=1737084066\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game is currently in its early demo stage and is under continuous development. Stay tuned for exciting updates, including new levels, modes, characters, outfits, and much more!</p><p class=\"bb_pa